description: The MSCI World Momentum Index (USD) (TRN) aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap companies from global developed markets with high momentum scores Weighted dependent on momentum characteristics such as performance in the previous 6 to 12 months Reviewed on a semi annual basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI World Momentum UCITS ETF 1C
